OL,3,C'It's meant to be such a nice time of
OL,4,Cyear, but for me it was petrifying'
OL,6,FA domestic abuse victim who escaped
OL,7,Fher violent partner on Boxing Day
OL,8,Fthree years ago is hoping her story
OL,9,Fwill give hope to others.
OL,11,FSophie - not her real name - suffered
OL,12,Fphysical and mental abuse at the hands
OL,13,Fof her former partner in Leeds.
OL,14,FAlthough she reported him to the
OL,15,Fpolice, he was never charged.
OL,17,FBut on 26 December 2021, she found the
OL,18,Fcourage to leave him.
