OL,3,C'It's meant to be such a nice time of
OL,4,Cyear, but for me it was petrifying'
OL,6,FThe 45-year-old said: "I had really
OL,7,Fhorrible experience around Christmas
OL,8,Ftime, I made a decision on Christmas
OL,9,FEve in 2021 that I needed to get out
OL,10,Fof the home I was living in with my
OL,11,Fabuser.
