OL,3,C'It's meant to be such a nice time of
OL,4,Cyear, but for me it was petrifying'
OL,6,F"I got in touch with my dad to ask him
OL,7,Fto collect me from a bus station on
OL,8,FBoxing Day. Once I had made that
OL,9,Fdecision and I knew that I was
OL,10,Fleaving, I just put all of my energy
OL,11,Finto getting through Christmas Day,
OL,12,Fwhich was a horrible day of this
OL,13,Fpressure where we're all meant to be
OL,14,Fcelebrating and joyous - it's just not
OL,15,Fthe reality for a lot of people."
OL,17,FCharity Leeds Women's Aid has been
OL,18,Fsupporting women and children
OL,19,Fsuffering from domestic abuse for over
OL,20,F50 years.
