OL,3,C'It's meant to be such a nice time of
OL,4,Cyear, but for me it was petrifying'
OL,6,FThe charity has a 24-hour helpline and
OL,7,Fhas reported a worrying pattern around
OL,8,Fthe Christmas period.
OL,10,FSophie added: "There's so much
OL,11,Fpressure around Christmas for
OL,12,Feverything to be just like the adverts
OL,13,Fon TV. The long build up and all the
OL,14,Ftime off work combined with alcohol
OL,15,Fand families kept in the house
OL,16,Ftogether means that daily routine just
OL,17,Fgoes out of the window, and it's an
OL,18,Fabsolute recipe for disaster.
