OL,3,C'It's meant to be such a nice time of
OL,4,Cyear, but for me it was petrifying'
OL,6,F"At this time of year, it's meant to
OL,7,Fbe such a nice time with everyone, but
OL,8,Ffor me it was petrifying.
OL,10,F"It was almost like groundhog day -
OL,11,Freliving the same thing over and over
OL,12,Fagain. I just decided I couldn't do it
OL,13,Fanymore.
OL,15,F"It was such a feeling of relief when
OL,16,FI got out. My mum held me and she
OL,17,Fseriously believed she wouldn't see me
OL,18,Falive again."
