OL,3,C'It's meant to be such a nice time of
OL,4,Cyear, but for me it was petrifying'
OL,6,FFor the past two years, the number of
OL,7,Fcalls to Leeds Women's Aid's helpline
OL,8,Fin January has been almost 50% higher
OL,9,Fthan the month before.
OL,11,FHannah Whyte, communications and
OL,12,Fmarketing manager, said: "Calls are
OL,13,Fhigh at the minute, but then they tend
OL,14,Fto drop off around Christmas day which
OL,15,Fis really worrying.
