OL,3,C'It's meant to be such a nice time of
OL,4,Cyear, but for me it was petrifying'
OL,6,F"So victims are getting through the
OL,7,Ffestive period and then in the days
OL,8,Fafterwards finding a way to call the
OL,9,Fservice. We're not saying Christmas
OL,10,Fcauses abuse, but it can intensify it
OL,11,Fwhere it already exists."
OL,13,FEven if a victim has managed to leave
OL,14,Ftheir partner, it doesn't always mean
OL,15,Fthe abuse ends there.
